---
title: Turkey Saag with Plum Tomatoes and Basmati Rice
description: We love good Turkey with Tomatoes and Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-saag-8dee1c5f-9942ef67.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/turkey-saag-5d286796a98784000f5958ab-39258edf.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/turkey-saag-5d286796a98784000f5958ab
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Indian
nutrition:
  calories: 525 kcal
  fat: 4 g
  saturated fat: 1 g
